description: North Carolina Flag socks are made out of combed cotton in our facility in North Carolina.  Our Dress Crew  socks are for all-around activities and have a carefully reinforced heel and toe for longer, more comfortable wear. For Every State sock Sold we are going to be donating a pair to the homeless and or veterans in that State
